----------
1. Aruchana A/P Selvaretnam, Priyadarshi Soumyaranjan Sahu, Madhusmita Sahu, Stephen Ambu. A review of concurrent infections of malaria and dengue in Asia. Asian Pac J Trop Biomed. 2016; 6(7): 633-8;
http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2221169116301757.
2. Charrel RN, Brouqui P, Foucault C, de Lamballerie X. Concurrent Dengue and Malaria. Infect Dis. 2005; 11(7): 1153-4; https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3371802/.
